// Unified Class 444 / 450 sprite and push-pull mappings.
// Shared approach:
// 1) choose local role sprites from articulated position and local cargo_subtype
// 2) choose reversed role sprites from mirrored articulated position and mirrored cargo_subtype
// 3) choose the reversed role chain from the mirrored unit type in mixed 444/450 formations

